body:
Not too sure if this is a bug or not, so I decided to write this issue regardless.
When updating and running the test files for the conferences module, it will return all of the conferences instead of just the two conferences given in the test file. 

Let's use `test_ncaaf_conferences.py` for example, it uses the ACC and SEC as the two sample conference inputs. It will say it's also expecting `{
                                'american': {
                                    'name': 'American Athletic Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'big-12': {
                                    'name': 'Big 12 Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                }, 
                                'big-ten': {
                                    'name': 'Big Ten Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'cusa': {
                                    'name': 'Conference USA',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'independent': {
                                    'name': 'Independent',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'mac': {
                                    'name': 'Mid-American Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'mwc': {
                                    'name': 'Mountain West Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                },
                                'pac-12': {
                                    'name': 'Pacific-12 Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                }, 
                                'sun-belt': {
                                    'name': 'Sun Belt Conference',
                                    'teams': {}
                                }
                              }` alongside with the ACC and SEC conferences. I was curious if this was the correct result or should it just only return the ACC and SEC and its respective teams.
